PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Our Gym App
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: How does the app track my workouts?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our app uses your phone's sensors and GPS to automatically detect and log your exercises, reps, and workout duration. You can also manually input your workouts for more precise tracking.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: Can I create custom workout plans?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Absolutely! You can create and save your own workout routines, or choose from our extensive library of pre-designed plans tailored to various fitness goals and experience levels.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: Is the app compatible with fitness wearables?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Yes, our app integrates seamlessly with most popular fitness wearables and smartwatches, allowing you to sync your heart rate, step count, and other vital stats for a comprehensive fitness overview.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: How can I track my progress over time?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: The app provides detailed progress reports, including graphs and charts that visualize your improvements in strength, endurance, and body measurements. You can also set and monitor personal goals to stay motivated.

FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Get answers to common queries about our gym app
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: How do I create a workout plan?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app offers a variety of pre-made workout plans or you can create custom plans by selecting exercises from our extensive database. Simply tap 'Create Plan' in the main menu to get started.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: Can I track my progress over time?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Absolutely! The app features a progress tracker that logs your workouts, weight, and measurements. You can view your progress through graphs and charts in the 'Progress' section.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: Is the app compatible with fitness wearables?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Yes, our app syncs with most popular fitness wearables and smartwatches to provide more accurate tracking of your workouts and daily activity.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: How do I access exercise demonstrations?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Each exercise in our database includes a video demonstration and written instructions. Simply tap on any exercise to view its details and demonstration.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: Can I connect with a personal trainer through the app?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: Yes, our app offers a feature to connect with certified personal trainers for personalized guidance and workout plans. You can book virtual sessions or in-person meetings directly through the app.
